t="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Taylor-Swift-performing-4.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Taylor-Swift-performing-4-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Taylor-Swift-performing-4-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Taylor-Swift-performing-4-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Taylor-Swift-performing-4-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Taylor-Swift-performing-4-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>因泰勒·斯威夫特 ( <a href="/artists/taylor-swift">Taylor Swift) 的</a>“Eras”巡演门票销售混乱而对 Live Nation 提起诉讼的主要原告已撤销诉讼。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/taylor-swift-the-eras-tour-concert-movie-3513715">“泰勒·斯威夫特：时代之旅”音乐会电影评论：这就是电影院（泰勒的版本）</a></strong></li></ul><p>早在2022年12月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-fans-sue-ticketmaster-over-the-eras-tour-ticket-controversy-3360134">来自13个州的十几名粉丝向洛杉矶县地方法院提起诉讼，</a>指控Ticketmaster在“经过验证的粉丝”预售过程中违反了加州卡特赖特法案和加州不公平竞争法。</p><p>粉丝们于 11 月 15 日首次获得<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-adds-17-more-shows-to-2023-the-eras-tour-tickets-3347682">北美巡演</a>门票。许多人反映，在开售之前，Ticketmaster 的在线队列等待时间过长，该公司网站出现中断，转售网站（包括 Ticketmaster 自己的网站）价格过高。 。</p><p> Ticketmaster 后来承认，他们面临着来自斯威夫特粉丝的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-eras-tour-ticketmaster-crash-3349775">“历史上前所未有的需求”</a> ，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-the-eras-tour-ticket-sale-cancelled-due-to-extraordinarily-high-demand-3351187">完全取消了一般销售</a>。斯威夫特本人<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-responds-ticketmaster-3351951">拒绝为公司“找借口”</a> ，称她和她的团队已确保该网站“可以满足这种需求”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3558511" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3558511" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3558511" src="